This is a Python inventory management system used as an AI evaluation environment on HUD RL platform.
The codebase has intentional bugs injected for evaluation purposes on specific branches.
Use Flask for API routes, SQLite for the database, and pytest for tests.
Branch structure: baseline (buggy code), test (pytest files), golden (correct working code).
When asked to inject a bug, make it subtle and realistic.
When asked to write tests, make them binary pass/fail with no partial credit.